# mpl-pe-pattern-monster

Pattern Monster for Matplotlib

https://mpl-pe-pattern-monster.readthedocs.io/


## Installation

You can install using `pip`:

```bash
pip install mpl_pe_pattern_monster
```

## Development Installation


```bash
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

